title: Shanghai aims to recuit 500,000 financial professions (Shanghai Municipal Government)
text: ( Source : Shanghai Municipal Government ) Shanghai plans to attract 500 , 000 financial professionals by 2020 to help build it into an international financial center. The government will provide all-round services and issue encouraging policies
